SELECT ? AS one FROM "domain_allows" WHERE "domain_allows"."domain" = $? LIMIT $?
SELECT ? AS one FROM "instances" WHERE "instances"."domain" = $? LIMIT $?

SELECT a.attname
  FROM (
         SELECT indrelid, indkey, generate_subscripts(indkey, ?) idx
           FROM pg_index
          WHERE indrelid = ?::regclass
            AND indisprimary
       ) i
  JOIN pg_attribute a
    ON a.attrelid = i.indrelid
   AND a.attnum = i.indkey[i.idx]
 ORDER BY i.idx

SELECT a.attnum, a.attname
FROM pg_attribute a
WHERE a.attrelid = ?
AND a.attnum IN (?)

SELECT distinct i.relname, d.indisunique, d.indkey, pg_get_indexdef(d.indexrelid), t.oid,
                pg_catalog.obj_description(i.oid, ?) AS comment, d.indisvalid
FROM pg_class t
INNER JOIN pg_index d ON t.oid = d.indrelid
INNER JOIN pg_class i ON d.indexrelid = i.oid
LEFT JOIN pg_namespace n ON n.oid = t.relnamespace
WHERE i.relkind IN (?, ?)
  AND d.indisprimary = ?
  AND t.relname = ?
  AND n.nspname = ANY (current_schemas(?))
ORDER BY i.relname
